aket, ai, mtis gadama mxares ("osetidan"), aeila veni ari ianvari.

that, look, a leadre of the German army, to Vadachkoria:

ale maxlyn metaur las, adaoria, i 'otoyra ceril ales:
This was a clever leader, this, Vadachkoria, and he had written him a letter:
es viani metauri iqo, ai, vadaoria, da dauceria cerili amas:
"ma... lix lok umal... umad nard lok lix oayen sua, ra, ramodenime sua,
"We are without food during somedays(and nights),
"ramdeni de-amea rac umelad varto, ra, ramdenime de-ame,
um... umelad arto, daexmaren lok sursats i bardebian lok".
we have no food, help us, give us food and we will yield prisoners".
umelad varto, dagvexmareto sursatit da gbardebito ("bardebiano")".
ali atqne alyrs, sayars i alyrs ubrana, ars, ere al ex k'r ???
He sent this (letter) with Kabardo-Balkarians and he gave an order to army, that this is a case,
es gaaana amat, qabardo-balqarelebs ("osebs") da ubrana, ars, rom es ikit rom???
atxe iara m xuax i lizi amx i darea amx, gugeite.
that they have not a guns and they have to go to us and he called here, us,
axla iarai ar akvt da ak ("akit") casvla da darea ak ("akit"), ventan.
ekas solbel mde i abel xunx i eeka las ei, elepon, mexe abelil mr las mayen,

main boebi ar iqo da abeli hkondat da imai iqo is, eleponi, raaca avi abeli iqo,
ere "ami lok li mine bedige i daexmaret lok".
so, "This is a case and help us"- he said.
rom "aseao veni sakme ("bedi da sakme") da dagvexmareto".
i 'ogxuryelex ami metxir xalx, esay geymedn, luntisa.
And so, they gathered us, all hunter people, whoever could come, in winter.
da egvribes ak monadire (dr. v. k. "mesatxevle") xalxi, visac egvelo, zamtari.
ar gkda, a, nai ai alar i zitqarl i ebdi lerek,
We got on fur coats, home-made shawls, home-made wool trousers and Pachichi(special shoes) and warm cloths.
kurkebi gvecva, in naksovi ali, in naksovi alis arvali da aiebi da tbili ansacmeli,
ere lacirte er rdad, mcxi dsa gda,
So, when we went for hunting, we were not cold.
rom roca sanadirod ("saixv{is}en") mivdiodit ("cavidodit"), ar gvcioda ("sicive ara gvkonda"),
txed-oxded gradus er las ei, qina.
That, it was 40-50 degrees of frost.
ormoc-ormocdaati gradusi rom iqo is, e, qinva.
ogyex ex eyre lazazd i sga loxzoznd lapuri ereali.
They took us with themselves to meet them and we met them at the Lapuri ravine.
cagviqvanes ("cagvies") ik mat ("imeebi{s}") esaxvedrad da evxvdit lapuris uelexilze.
ale i uida ol i al oli laesgnun loxzoznd sga.
This unfusible ice! And we met them at the middle of glacier.
es gaumdnari ("auebi") qinuli da am mqinvaris uamde mivegebet.

One man died at that place, we found him only in summer,
erti aci ikve gardaicvala, mxolod gazapxulze viovet
da amoviqvanet ("amovzidet") uve eseni ven, isini.

They got on high boots and boots become frosen, the boots are not like our Suni shoes (Chapuli),
ekmebi ecvat da ekmebs xelad qinavs, iseti i ara, ven unis pexsacmeli ("apulebi"),
cerek gixlda nay aa, cereks xonxndad na... nanxnars xaldad nay eys.
look, we knew also tomi, we put in boots tomi, we called it lanchi.
e, tomi vicodit ven idev, toms vunevdit, lanebs veaxdit ven imas.
ebdid lrek eayd, ere mcxi dma, op gar ggda nay.
We were dressed so warm that we were not cold, we were covered only with steam.
ise tbilad acmulebi viqavit, rom ar gvcioda ("sicive ara"), mxolod opli gvasxamda ("gvedga") ven.
ere "gugey alib lok xeqda exu yed i alyr lok imnar xau?"
that: "That if I have ten ones like you and I don't need these(soldiers) at all.
rom "tkvennairebi mqavdeso ("ven qalibio hqavda") erti ati da eseni ristvis mindao ("enuvis")?"
xoa qinol lasx mag, mara m lasx eyi i lrek i ami gadaarinet i 'nqidd eyr.
All of them were good boys, but they were not dressed so well and we saved them down.
argi biebi iqvnen suqvelani, magram ar iqvnen iseti acmulebi da ase gadavarinet da amoviqvanet ("amovianet") isini.
It was the army of the 7th sotnia.
i ildoel logemx eno tarobad, aasy daca medlar.
And the government gave us rewards, they decorated us with the medals of Caucausus Defence.
da ildoebi gadmogvca ("mogvces") mere mtavrobam, avasiis dacvis medlebi.
mere, eno anrda aa gamarebis ati clis, oci, ozdaati, ormoci, alyr mag miebul mua.
After, then comes the rewards to the 10th, 20th, 30th, 40th anniversaries of the victory, I have got all of them
mere, mere modioda isev gamarvebis ati clis, oci, ocdaati, ormoci, eseni qvela miebuli makvs.
romis monacileoba, olmeurneobysa, proni da proni zurg lasx eka gaertianebul.
At that time, the rewards were given for the work, for the good work in the community, for the participation un the front and in the back of front - everything these were united.
romis monacileoba, olmeurneobai, proni da pronis zurgi iqvnen main gaertianebuli.
eka es clil xua, romis unari... rom minimum gamomuaebul, s laxmx ensia.
At that time, a pension was given to everybody, who did his bit, who was able to work.
main visac cvlili akvs, romis unari... romis minimumi gamomuavebuli, qvelas misces ensia.
s autales ali, omi monacileob saitx i ensia laxmx s eyrs, zuralls i arsi.
They give this to everybody, well, and a pension was given to all of them, to men and to women.
qvelas autvales es, ai, omis monacileobis saitxi da ensia misces qvelas imat ("imeebs"), kalebs da acebsac.
_ Did they give you a pension?
_ miy, monacil ensia mua miy, semedyoxud manat, eno ara lar 'emkimx aa
_ Me also, I also have the pension for the participation(in war), 35 maneti, after they added also 8 lari.
_ mec, monacilis ensia makvs mec, ocdatxutmei maneti, mere rva lari damimaes idev
i mara dsma xepsi al ensils, olil li suru.
But this pension is nothing, it is too few.
da magram araperi araa es ensia ("ensias"), meismead coaa.
ekad yer mun ensia, omunisare iysa, yedsemi tumn mun, ara meo peks xiqdis
The pension, which I had before, during the communists, I had 13 tumani, I could buy 8 sacks of wheat.
manamde rom mkonda ensia, omunisebis xeli, camei tumani mkonda, rva omara pkvils vqidulobdi da
i ami miga yexs xun ensia i e gixun exu tea ensia zayni-zayn.
So, my wife also had her pension and the one month's pension was enough for us from yearto year.
ase ems meules ("cols") hkonda ensia da gvqopnida ("ise gveqara") erti tvis ensia clidan clamde.
Other things, other things we had also.
atxe dsma, igid manat er 'embinex i, yered, yer... yeru tumaneltei aqidx atxe rigiti ensil.
No more now, they began with 7 maneti and, well, now, an ordinal pension goes up to 20 tumani.
axla araperi, vidi manetit rom daicqes da, ai, oc, or tumnamde aiqvanes axla rigiti ensia ("ensiebi").
_ We have too funny pension now.
_ So was, my dear, our news(affairs).
